Daly_City.KFSF-DT: KFSF-DT, virtual channel 66 (UHF digital channel 34), is a UniMás owned-and-operated television station licensed to Vallejo, California, United States and serving the San Francisco Bay Area. The station is owned by the Univision Local Media subsidiary of Univision Communications, as part of a duopoly with San Francisco-licensed Univision owned-and-operated station KDTV-DT (channel 14). The two stations share studios located at 1940 Zanker Road in San Jose; KFSF maintains transmitter facilities located at Sutro Tower in San Francisco.
